(7467, 1979, 881, 1, '交心', '曾經以「向前行」這首歌轟動一時的林強，2007在網路上推出了單曲「交心」。這是大塊文化董事長郝明義所發起的「ucareicare讓好病人遇上好醫生」(改善醫病關係公益行動)主題曲。這幾年，林強幾乎是「封口」狀態，大量投入電子音樂/電影配樂，只有少量地在廣告＆電子舞曲中，偶開金口，點綴幾許。這首交心又將我們拉回了1990的林強，舒服非常的抒情民謠小品，林強的唱腔依然溫暖有力無可替代，對萬物的關懷依然一以貫之。林強一直非常支持「CC授權」，長久參與CC活動，此次，獻出此曲支持【CABACA】可謂義正辭嚴。這首歌已經在網上流行很久，第一次實體出版。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '交心 不用講出嘴　關心別人 疼惜自己\r\n面對日頭 向前去　勇敢體驗 生活滋味\r\n人生 難得結緣　愛別人 親像愛自己\r\n陰暗烏影不如意　像露水遇到日頭 會化無去\r\n\r\n雖然外頭風雨不止　雖然心頭猶然怨氣\r\n凡事看得開　順其自然歡歡喜喜\r\n保佑咱身邊所有的人　都平安順遂\r\n\r\n人生親像一齣戲　愛心滿天邊\r\n敬愛自然心善意　宇宙萬物同慈悲\r\nYou care I care\r\n生.老.病痛　好心善報終有時', '', 291, '林強', '林強', '林強', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:33:48', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7468, 1979, 881, 2, '總是會出頭', '2004年開始，朱頭皮儼然是「CC授權」親善大使，親自撰寫演唱「CC台灣主題曲」，四處演講，主辦多次CC音樂會。這次，CC亞洲樂團的CABACA專輯，朱頭皮自然而然擔任製作總兼。只不過，豬改不了吃頭皮屑，這首總是會出頭動用30種語言長達7分鐘的史詩大河巨作依然嬉笑怒罵多所影射尖酸刻薄，搞笑是一定要的。任何一首偉大的作品必然誕生在多災多難的時代＆所在。全世界忙著對抗「全球暖化」，台灣來到一個新時代，在民進黨交出政權的2008的台灣，諷刺所有政治人物也挖苦自己。老藍調的新生命，台灣特性之於亞洲特性之於世界節奏，世界性的CC運動，都在這個歌裡。這個歌，聽起來就像是在東南亞逛街會聽到的路邊小曲，日本/韓國/台灣也都通用的一種「俗豔恰恰亞洲調」，「俗閣有力」！基本架構是相傳誕生於美國密嘻嘻比河流域傳統12小節藍調。這個歌，既有台灣本土色彩，又有東南亞＆日韓氣味，加上國際化的韻律節拍，世界級傳世作品就這一首。「嘻嘻亞洲樂團」要幹嘛？豈不是要展現所謂「亞洲特性」嗎？都學美國人/英國人的話，那我們還搞個啥屁。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '（1）台語(TAIWANESE).\r\n一兩三四五六七八九.(1、2、3、4、5、6、7、8、9).\r\n鼠牛虎兔龍蛇馬羊狗.(rat,cow,tiger,bunny,dragon,snake,horse,sheep,dog).\r\nA.B.C.D.狗咬豬咬猴.(a.b.c.d. dog bite pig bite monkey).\r\n食銅食鐵食金食銀食夠夠.(eat everything, even eat me!).\r\n橫柴入灶穩龜也食未消.(you gone too far, I can’t take it anymore).\r\n打一支九萬放炮予汝到.(ok, I just let go, all on you).\r\n（p.s.）「九萬」是「馬英九＆蕭萬長」2008年參與台灣總統大選時的吉祥物，將麻將牌「九萬」做成手機吊飾，比喻.馬英「九」＆蕭萬「長」.果然.胡牌！\r\nhttp://blog.yam.com/crysis/article/13447707\r\n\r\n(2)…台語(TAIWANESE).\r\n好康也總抱.歹康也走繳.(you take good all, leave bad behind).\r\n是激空空嘛是咧起踍.(you are crazy? Out of mind?).\r\n鄭憨憨汝閣兼博臭.(Pretend? Not obey rules).\r\n神秘的微笑. 厚道不厚道.(secret smile, amiable? Hostile ? clement? strict ?)\r\n愛台灣啦.阿狗.阿斗烏白鬥.([love TAIWAN] just on your mouth? Whatever you do count on this excuse).\r\n十世人汝嘛還袂了.(can you pay this back after 10 generations).\r\n（p.s.）「神秘的微笑」可能是在罵邱義仁吧？\r\nhttp://blog.udn.com/kris88/1840078\r\n\r\n(3)gtr solo duo.\r\n\r\n(4) 台灣原住民.（TAIWAN ABORIGINAL）.\r\n(阿美族) (amis).giahu saligaga.你好. [how do you do].\r\n(排灣) (paiwan).maljimalji de Jesu sama. 感謝耶穌. Thank JESUS.\r\n(布農族) (bunun)mihomisang, ma las da bong.你好. [誇功宴] (the feast).\r\n(魯凱)rukai, (達悟)tawu, (卑南)puyuma,.(tribe name, means:human).\r\n(太魯閣)taluku, (鄒)tsou, (賽夏)Saishiat. (tribe name, means:human).\r\n(泰雅爾) (tayal). Li Mui So La Li Mui Yo.(traditional aboriginal folk).\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：台語&原住民：共11種】\r\n\r\n（5）台灣客家話（TAIWAN hakka）\r\n神經砰.勾魔.記得否？（神經病.搞怪死小孩.記得嗎？）(nuts, punky, remember?)\r\n安茲謝.承蒙.頭路.（謝謝. 謝謝.）(工作.工作)(thank you)(work).\r\n月光華華.花樹下.唱山歌.(月光亮亮) (花樹下)（唱山歌）.\r\n頭擺頭擺.細妹安獎.（以前以前.小姐漂亮）(log time ago)(girl beautiful).\r\n沒共樣的人.看破沒彩工.(不一樣的人.看破了還是無用)(different people)(still useless when you see it thru).\r\n阿姆好否.(阿母.好不好.)(mama, ok?).\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共12種】\r\n\r\n（6）(華語).(TAIWAN chinese) .\r\n現在這些小孩唱個啥東西.聽了半天也聽不懂.了.(what those young kids singing what today?).\r\n流行音樂.流行文化.走到這般地步無法進入.了.(pop-music, pop-culture, come to this step?).\r\n我老了還是我累了.我笨了還是我慢了.(am I old? Am I tired? Am I stupid? Am I slow?).\r\n小時候那些偉大的音樂.20世紀少年.去哪裡？了.(the great music of my childhood like [20th century boy], where is it?)\r\n到了21世紀.少年們已經不再拯救世界.了.(now it’s 21th century, young boys don’t want to save the world).\r\n把馬子.搞kuso.危險的時候.趕快跑.了.(get some chicks, do some idiot, gotta run when danger).\r\n（p.s.）20 世紀少年[20th century boy]是70年代英國華麗搖滾天團-雷克斯龍(T-REX)的名曲.1999年開始.日本漫畫家-浦澤直樹.以此為典故.畫出暢銷數百萬本的連環漫畫，2008年八月30號，《20世紀少年》真人電影版三部曲的第一集就要上映。\r\nhttp://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/20%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4\r\nhttp://mycartoon.my-cartoon.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=680&Itemid=121\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共13種】\r\n\r\n（7）.(台語)(TAIWANese).\r\n想起細漢時.「史豔文」看甲津津有味.(when I was a kid, I watched Taiwan puppet tv show).\r\n劉三.哈麥兩齒.醉彌勒.猶原在眼前.(all characters on my eyes now).\r\n慢慢大漢.即知影.布袋戲的音樂原來是「出埃及記」.(I grow up then realize, many Taiwan puppet music score are international pop hits,「Exodus」).\r\n娶某生子了後.霹靂布袋戲煞看無啥有.(after marriage, have kids, the modern Taiwan puppet can’t catch my eyes ).\r\n紅甲變電影.紅甲去美國.講是台灣國寶.(the new modern Taiwan puppet was big hit, go to big screen, go to U.S.A. should be TAIWAN national treasure).\r\n「霹靂火」紅甲翻過.一分鐘麻看袂落.(some hot hit tv pogram so popular among olds & kids, but I just can never get in over 1 minute).\r\n\r\n（8）（布袋戲.用語）. (TAIWANese).\r\n三好加一好=四好！啦.（3 plus 1 equals 4, you go to hell）.\r\n囝仔人有耳無嘴有腳穿袂放屁.（kids, listen, don’t speak, don’t use you butt hole）.\r\n講甲汝捌.嘴鬚著打結.（my beard will got tied to let you know）.\r\n我空莽空. 我草鞋顛倒嚨.（I’m stupid but I know what cc is）.\r\n有代誌著有代誌.無代誌我負責.啦.（I just wanna do this, if something happen, is on you）.\r\n\r\n（9）（布袋戲.用語）. (TAIWANese). .\r\n為前途.辜不二三衷.；.（for the future, can noy but）.\r\n媽媽請汝麥悲傷..（mama, please don’t be sad）.\r\n毋倘傷風也無通痛風；.（don’t catch cold, don’t catch gout）.\r\n我送汝一咧純陽掌.（I send you a gamesmanship）.\r\n(p.s. 純陽掌=「雲洲大儒俠.史豔文」之絕招.).\r\n緊張緊張.刺激刺激.恐怖恐怖.；（nervious, acridness, horror）.\r\n預知結果如何.繼續給聽落.便知分曉..（keep listening, you will find out）\r\n\r\n（10）中國華語.(Chinese chinese).\r\n嘻嘻哈哈搞啥的.(cc ha ha, what the folk?).\r\n搞了幾年了.有沒起色.(many years passing by, pump what up?).\r\n碰見熟人打招呼.(meet familiar friends, say hello).\r\n怎麼樣？.咳. 「湊合」.(how do you do? What’s up with your cc-ing?).\r\n「湊合」「湊合」「湊合」「湊合」.(well,…you tell me.).\r\n原來.自由並不那麼容易得.的.(so, freedom is not so free).\r\n(p.s.). (碰見熟人打招呼.怎麼樣？.咳. 湊合!)學習自中國北京搖滾漢子【崔健】1998專輯『無能的力量』第一曲「混子」.不敢略美.特註明之.（2007年.熱天.【崔健】首次「登台」.唱「海洋音樂祭」.要求台下觀眾跟他大爺起鬨.當崔哥哥講到「怎麼樣？」.我們這些滾動的混蛋就得大呼小叫「湊合」！成了大夥兒最樂的段子.）\r\nhttp://blog.roodo.com/muzikland/archives/1688911.html\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共14種】\r\n\r\n（11）日文. (Japanese).\r\naligado goziemasida = thank you very much (非常感謝).\r\nMinasan gokulosama(大家辛苦了)（bother everybody）.\r\nOhaieyo, konbonwa, Wagalimasida(早安.晚上好.我知道)(good morning, good evening, I know).\r\nHonda toyota Yamaha.(本田. 豐田.山葉). (great japan motor company)\r\nhandolu penzi lolieba = 方向盤, 尖嘴鉗, 鑼斯起子 . hadel. Clam, screwdriver\r\nwadasiwa buda-adama-kawa = my name is Pig-Head-Skin.(我是豬頭皮).\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共15種】\r\n\r\n（12）.\r\n(korean)Anihaseyo, kansalamida= hello, thank you.（韓文.你好.謝謝）\r\n(korean)salanheyyo , JEON Ji-hyun=I love you, 全智賢.（韓文.我愛你, 전지현）\r\n(korean)LG, Samsung, kimchi, bin bin bon泡菜.韓國石鍋拌飯.（life is good）(韓國三星)（good food）\r\n(thailand) kapunclup sawadika= thank you, how do you do (泰語)(謝謝, 你好).\r\n(indonisian)delimakaci cinta !! =thank you, love you(印尼語)(謝謝, 愛你).\r\n(Hong Kong)多謝多謝.猴塞雷 (香港話).謝謝.好厲害.\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共19種】\r\n\r\n（13）\r\n(Malaysian)terima kasi(thank you)馬來語(謝謝).\r\n(Malaysian)selamat digao(goodbye)馬來語(再會).\r\n(Malaysian)Saia cinta alamu(I love you)馬來語(我愛你).\r\n(Filipino/Tagalog)mabúhay(hello),salámat(thank you)(菲律賓話)你好,謝謝.\r\n(Filipino/Tagalog)paálam(goodbye),mahál kitá(i love you)(菲律賓話)再會,愛你.\r\nWow, So many too learn(阿. 好多要學阿).\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共22種】\r\n\r\n（14）\r\nThe more you learn, （學得越多）.\r\nthe more you know. （懂得越多）.\r\nThe more you know, （知道得更多）.\r\nthe more you forget. （忘得更多）.\r\nThe more you forget, the less you know. （忘得更多）. （知道更少）.\r\nSo why bother to learn.（所以.幹嘛要學阿）.\r\n（p.s.）(U.K. Cambridge University school motto). (英國劍橋大學校訓)\r\n\r\n（15）euro(歐系語)…\r\n義大利文Ciao(hello), Pavarotti, giorgio armani（italiano）.\r\n西班牙文 hola(hello), La Cucaracha (Cockroach) , Te amo (I love you) (español).\r\n法文, bonjour(hello), je t''aime(i love you), dolce & gabbana（French）.\r\n德文, Guten tag. (hello), danke schön(thx a lot),achtung baby(attention),（dutch）(german).\r\nTwo oh oh seven(2007), Croatia (克羅埃西亞).\r\nTwo oh oh eight（2008）,NIPPON（日本）.\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共27種】\r\n\r\n（16）english(英文) .\r\nCREATE ! NOT SO HARD !（創作不很難）.\r\nI''LL LOVE YOU with ALL MY HEART.（我全心全意愛你）.\r\nCOME ON, YOU NEED TO GET A START.（來吧.開始吧）.\r\nCREATIVE, EVERY PARK.（有創意的人.四處都有）.\r\nCOMMONS ALL WE GOT.（我們都一家人）.\r\noh MY GOD!!（創意公眾.CC.我的天.）.\r\n\r\n（17）CABACAIN (卡巴卡語)\r\nHI HI HA HA WU BA DA.\r\nDI DI DA DA KU SA LA.\r\nLI LI LA LA DU MA SA.\r\nSI SI SA SA BU KA BA.\r\nBI BI BA BA LU GA CHA.\r\nCHI CHI CHA CHA CA BA CA.\r\n卡巴卡語.\r\n嘻嘻哈哈吳爸打.\r\n滴滴答答哭啥啦.\r\n哩哩拉拉肚馬沙.\r\n嘻嘻沙沙補卡巴.\r\n逼逼八八盧甲掐.\r\n七妻掐掐卡巴卡.\r\n（p.s.） [卡巴卡]是個「未來國」=無煙. 無碳. 無廢棄物. 無惡. 無邪. 無爭執. 自然能源循環再利用. 每天沒事幹. 只能製造愛情. 相互讚美. 唱歌跳舞.= [CABACA] Is The Biggest Country Of The Future, no smoke. no carbon, no litter, no evil, no wicked, no quarrel, nature resources recycle reuse, nothing to do, only make love, praise each other, sing, dance…\r\n有時.卡巴卡會派他們的飛行器來拜訪我們.=Sometimes [CABACA] Send Their Flying Object To Visit Us,\r\nwww.streetvoice.com.tw/cabaca\r\nhttp://cabaca.org\r\n\r\n【統計：已使用語言數：共28種】\r\n\r\n(18)（hokkanese）（新加坡/馬來/東南亞華人之福建話）\r\n卡巴卡！累過頭. (doing CABACA is overloaded).\r\n船慢慢駛嘛到橋頭.（this ship is slow, but, keep sailing anyway）.\r\n阿撒埠祿驚人比較.（nothing compares to you, all cc-laborers）.\r\n蹲佇咧便所惦惦哭.（squatted in a toilet, weeping slightly）.\r\n趴小姐艱苦第一熬.（it’s hard, not easy to get any resource）.\r\n趴拼.總是會出頭！（just do it, getting harder, every dog has his day）.', '', 417, '朱頭皮', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:34:46', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7469, 1979, 881, 3, 'Freedom Zen', '莫尚是南非音樂家，幾年前來台教英文，遇到真愛，跟彰化姑娘訂終身，居台中。張睿銓是英文老師，出版過兩張繞舌專輯，歌詞批判性十足，堪稱開台以來最殺。此曲(空禪)是莫尚拿手的沙發慵懶舞曲(lounge)，配上社會派詩般美麗的歌詞：「妨害治安被捕，傳講真理被關，尋找真愛被處決…」，使用舒服的音樂來批判掌握權力者，高明!', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '\r\nI''m arrested for a breach of the peace, uh-huh\r\nI''m arrested for a breach of the peace, uh-huh\r\nI''m imprisoned for the truth that I speak\r\nWill be executed for the love that I seek, uh-huh\r\n\r\nMy friend''s a teacher. Sylvie wears this black T-shirt\r\nBought from Reporters without Borders, recorders of marauders\r\nIt''s five handcuffs joined above 2008\r\nPay online, and your shipment arrives in fourteen days\r\nBut when I''m placing an order on this free-speech website\r\nIt''s taken over by the interface in Chinese Simplified\r\nPropaganda''s never simplified, can only be vandalized\r\nI orchestrate lyrical drive-bys\r\nBlacklisted writers ain''t woke up from the abyss\r\nHow much of your justice was purchased by those in mists?\r\nSonic death threats received ''cause she says "Shame on the police"\r\nIntelligence is openly silenced by violence on reprise\r\nRich folks and politicians perform intercourse on TV\r\nMetaphors that tease me accept the passports of them landlords\r\nGranted entry to my country self-willingly spelled backward\r\nThe benumbed wolf in the Arctic licks the blade that protrudes from the snow\r\nSuicide show. Tongue cut, feast of blood, body picked up\r\nBy hunters who hide to maintain the status quo\r\nGunshots heard from the other side of the war zone\r\nThousands of kilos away but near like a ring tone\r\nFreedom of speech becomes a figure of speech, shown\r\nBy the greed of a leech and a dog on a leash\r\n\r\nI''m arrested for a breach of the peace, uh-huh\r\nI''m arrested for a breach of the peace, uh-huh\r\nI''m imprisoned for the truth that I speak\r\nWill be executed for the love that I seek, uh-huh\r\n\r\nAncient mentality created solely by homo sapiens\r\nPillaging their own kind across space and time\r\nNeither animal nor divine, breathed into your blood\r\nWhether you''re deaf, dumb, or blind\r\nHe who sees from the side has eight eyes\r\nMeditate and transform into the late night\r\nAdmire cherry blossoms from two breaths away\r\nEnter the tea room disarmed and learn the Way\r\nDrink water from the well, elixir for any pain felt\r\nMy steel''s long sheathed so heaven isn''t hell\r\nTriumph is fulfilled when no one''s killed\r\nBut life prevails when it ends. I''m Death himself\r\nTolerance for police brutality in a Zen style\r\nFragrance of mortal sacrifices to defend smiles\r\nOf those women and children who are precious and innocent\r\nWhen traces of murder and terror seem but evident\r\nThe earthquake distracted attention, not a precedent\r\nBut didn''t stop the soldiers from butchering more dissidents\r\nDonations channeled to corruption and military weapons\r\nVengeance is yours, Lord, witnessed with eyes open\r\nReflections of the sun, moon, and stars on the ocean\r\nParadigms are shifting, huh, in constant motion\r\nThey say all the answers are written on the hidden leaves\r\nRead carefully, and you can be truly free\r\n\r\nI''m arrested for a breach of the peace, uh-huh\r\nI''m arrested for a breach of the peace, uh-huh\r\nI''m imprisoned for the truth that I speak\r\nWill be executed for the love that I seek, uh-huh', '', 277, '莫尚, 張睿銓', '莫尚', '張睿銓', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:45:50', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7470, 1979, 881, 4, 'Naluwan House', '拷秋勤是近年備受好評之台灣本土戲曲嘻哈派，2008得了金曲獎兩項提名。首先，拷秋勤將這首Naluwan House佈到cabaca工作網，然後，MoShang加了一些東西上去，然後，教英文的台北女孩Sonja V.加上甜美的歌聲。「愛是個謎，是哲學，是邏輯，是理論… 愛是人生，是旅程…」。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, 'Love is a mystery, you call it philosophy.\r\nThe logical theory, anticipation is well conceived.\r\nLovers embracing, we hunger for unity.\r\nThe chemistry in remixing, there is no boundary for you and me.\r\n\r\nWorld should be healing,\r\nLove is what we''re needing.\r\nWe all need to fight for the rising.\r\nWorld must be healing,\r\nLove is how we''re feeling.\r\nUniversal language we are one.\r\n\r\nWe are on friend, we are one.\r\nWe are one friend, we are love.\r\n\r\nLife is a journey, the light of humanity.\r\nThe happiness in remixing , we bound together just you and me.', '', 244, '拷秋勤, Sonja V.', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:46:37', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7471, 1979, 881, 5, 'Walking Tall', 'Monbaza可曰台灣電音教父，投入音樂與藝術創作領域二十載不悔，近年的音樂創作大量載入民族聲響，溫暖了冷冰冰的電子地窖。此首Walking Tall已經無從分類：洋味十足的管樂大樂團伴奏、古箏、笛子、二胡…大戰，肥滿飽足的貝斯線，百人敲擊樂器大排檔，電子音效四竄，民族吟唱、薩克斯風也來嘎一腳。加上馬來西亞的吉他之神Sudev(蘇德夫)火辣的電吉他，恰似嘉年華開場歡樂曲，又似歷來奧運選手進場必放之亢奮舞曲。', '2008-08-11 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 3, '', '', 191, 'Monbaza', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-08-11 12:47:08', '2015-03-12 13:34:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
